      "created_at": "2023-08-03T18:25:03.670Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I would strongly support this call. Actually, I\u2019d like to be able to swipe lower 4 fields block just like I do on my Garmin edge in order to see metrics grouped at different level - either whole WO or interval.</p>\n<p>Fields I\u2019d like to be able to see (in addition to those we have):</p>\n<p>for entire workout:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>NP</li>\n<li>TSS</li>\n<li>avg cadence</li>\n<li>work in kcal</li>\n</ul>\n<p>for current interval:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>avg cadence</li>\n<li>target cadence is there is one (I know about color)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Thanks much, Alex!</p>",
